      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this exemplary vehicle, currently held in absolute showroom condition. This specimen represents a rare convergence of meticulous maintenance and unrivaled preservation, featuring an unblemished exterior and an interior that retains its original factory luster. Mechanically beyond reproach and showing no signs of wear, this motorcar offers a singular opportunity for the discerning enthusiast to acquire an investment-grade example of automotive excellence.",
